SELECT id, ava_file, badges, blocked, bot_owner, email, email_confirmed,
  friends, groups, mfa_secret, name, password, pending_in, pending_out, public,
  salt, status, status_text, tag
  FROM yamkadb.users
  LIMIT 500;

SELECT id, ava_file, badges, blocked, bot_owner, email, email_confirmed,
  friends, groups, mfa_secret, name, password, pending_in, pending_out, public,
  salt, status, status_text, tag
  FROM yamkadb.users
  LIMIT 500;
update users set friends=null where id>0 allow filtering;
update users set friends=null where tag>0 allow filtering;
